困擾藏在心裡，因鬱結和壓力積存得太多太久，到情緒爆發時可能已超出你所能控制的程度。<br />\n<br />\n你不如停一停，到我們的網站  <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7IgxAEvDk8dns9g3QPAGj3dU%3D&h=cffba18c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>  。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：下午4時至凌晨1時；星期六、日及公眾假期：晚上８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"effbd3c27c6d65b4f0f466dc8e01d519e8e280e5","tid":2280940,"uid":225828,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"17cddfa1cc109db38082420c23b403b9fa08bace","tid":2280940,"uid":135942,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"20378b7d024a0c2ac2aa9968fa2a10446ac1522e","tid":2280940,"uid":58963,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T01:48:29.000Z","msg":"巴打冷靜，不如講下咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T01:53:11.000Z","msg":"絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我估應該係情緒問題掛 <br />\n捱到一次 捱唔到第二次<br />\n呢種諗法係會返黎㗎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c3d4666364e662cf89a4e8fca8f5d28d745c2a","tid":2280940,"uid":21234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"effbd3c27c6d65b4f0f466dc8e01d519e8e280e5","tid":2280940,"uid":225828,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"17cddfa1cc109db38082420c23b403b9fa08bace","tid":2280940,"uid":135942,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"20378b7d024a0c2ac2aa9968fa2a10446ac1522e","tid":2280940,"uid":58963,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T01:48:29.000Z","msg":"巴打冷靜，不如講下咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T01:53:11.000Z","msg":"絲打<img src=\"/